headline: Workday (NasdaqGS:WDAY) Expands Footprint in Iconic Empire State Building
summary: Workday (NasdaqGS:WDAY) has recently expanded its lease at the Empire State Building, marking significant business expansion into 39,069 square feet of space. Despite this positive development, the company's stock price experienced a 2% decline over the past week, while the broader market remained stable and showed a 5.7% increase over the past year.
